name: Samira Patel
summary: Samira Patel is a 28-year-old woman who works as a software engineer in the tech industry. She currently lives in Los Angeles, California but hails from Mumbai, India. She is a graduate of Stanford University. She identifies as heterosexual and speaks both English and Hindi. Her core values are Equity, Inclusion, and Social Justice. Her interests mainly revolve around coding, reading, cooking, and hiking. She follows the Hindu faith and politically leans liberal. Samira is seeking a long-term monogamous relationship. She does not currently have children but wishes to in the future. She owns a dog and is moderately active, sometimes indulging in drinks but refrains from smoking and drug use. Her personality type is ISFJ, and her zodiac sign is Scorpio. She hopes to meet a man aged between 28 and 35 who does not currently have children but also wants them in the future, leads an active lifestyle, indulges in occasional drinking, and abstains from smoking and drug use.
